postcontent:
WTT gold and mostly silver for firearms, parts and maybe some optics.  Please let me know exactly what you have, how much gold and/or silver you want for it and where you are located as this will save us both time.  If you message me with "S&W AR-15?" or "Interested in a Glock or Beretta?" or similar messages, I will politely respond with "Thanks, but I'll pass", since I don't know what model(s) you are offering, details on what it does or does not come with and you did not let me know what you want for it.  I am not interested in retail prices, I can buy new online anytime.
In gold I have some 1/10oz. bars.  In silver I have 1oz. Eagles, rounds, bars and some 10oz. bars, let me know the deal.
Prefer cash, but may consider trades.  Please be specific on exactly what you have and want to do up front, straight trade, trade +/- cash or other??  If you don't mention a cash amount or other either way, I will assume you want a straight trade.
Mostly interested in semi-autos, will consider others, depending.  Stripped lowers, nice AR/AK triggers, quality lightweight 12"-15" AR rail and 12"+/- AR-10 rail.  FosTech Echo or Franklin BFS Gen 3 triggers.  
AR 9mm with 5"-8" barrel, 5.56 with 8"-10" barrel and 7.62x39 with 8"-10" barrel, medium weight barrels preferred, uppers or complete.  9mm lower, complete or stripped(preferred).  2-3 Law Tactical Gen 3-M or Dead Foot Arms folding adapters.  2-3 KAK Shockwave kits.  Side-charging upper receivers for 5.56 & 9mm.  New factory Glock 9mm 31+ round normal capacity mags.  I can get complete PSA and similar uppers shipped really cheap, but want to try and trade for some first.  No BCG needed on the 5.56.
1oz. silver bars, rounds or Eagles.  Value needs to equal cash price, let me know the details.
Vortex Strike Eagle 1-6x, PA 1-6x ACSS 5.56/.308 & 7.62x39 reticles, other similar 1-6+x and 1-4x with nice clear glass and true 1x, QD mounts are a plus and some longer range scopes in 4-16x, 6-24x etc., needs to have good eye relief and clear glass.  I have some Nikon M-308 and M-223 4-16x I've picked up for around $300 in excellent condition and a little more with quality mounts.  I've been pleased with these, but open to others like Vortex etc.  Maybe a couple of nice micro red dots.  Not interested in retail prices, I can buy online any time at retail.FTF or I can ship insured once I have your item.  No lowballers, no flakes, no POS scammers and no BS!
